    modified_response: "I will create `/src/components/DashboardScreen.tsx`. This file governs the primary Ethereal Journal diary, including an interactive calendar timeline, entry creation with text or simulated voice recording, a list of current journal entries (pre-populated with the iconic mock reflection from the prompt), and settings toggles for a completely functional user experience."
