  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Defining App Entry Point**\n\nI\'m now focusing on completely defining `/src/App.tsx`. The goal is for it to handle user authentication and routing. I\'ll check for an active user in state; rendering the `OnboardingScreen` if none, otherwise `DashboardScreen`. Everything will be wrapped by the `PhoneFrame` component.\n\n\n**Refining Dashboard Implementation**\n\nI\'m now implementing the `DashboardScreen`, ensuring it handles entries, loading and saving to local storage. It will pre-populate a default entry and manage `AISummarySheet`\'s open/close state, sending POST requests to `/api/summarize`. The focus is now on perfectly aligning imports in `App.tsx` and incorporating the user headshot URL: `https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC5m7o5vlfMJLuMytcnN`.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will now implement `/src/App.tsx` to serve as the master coordinator for Ethereal Journal. It manages authentication state, diary entry lists (syncing to localStorage), coordinates fetching the server-side dynamic Gemini API summaries with full custom refinement capabilities, and wraps everything in our elegant Android mock `PhoneFrame`."
