ont-sans` as the primary font, as shown in the design HTML.\n\n\n**Updating Theme Variables**\n\nI\'m now focusing on mapping the \"Vibrant Palette\" directly to the `@theme` variables within `/src/index.css`. I\'m going to set `--color-journal-primary` to `#0F172A` or `#1E293B` for text, paired with `#F43F5E` for brand highlights and gradients. The secondary color will be `#6366F1`, while teal shifts to `#F43F5E` or `#10B981`. I will set the background to `#FDFCFB` or `#F8FAFC`, surface to white, and card-low to `#F1F5F9`.\n\n\n"
