sual appeal and thematic consistency. Specifically, I\'m focusing on the container\'s background, incorporating a subtle visual style. I\'m also styling the icon, text hierarchy and badges. I\'m focusing on lines 196 to 226 in `AISummarySheet.tsx` to enhance this section.\n\n\n**Integrating Milestone Section**\n\nI am now focusing on the Milestone section, refining its visual presentation for enhanced clarity and aesthetic appeal. I\'ve updated the border color to indigo, adjusted the background to be more visually appealing, and am re-styling the bullet points to ensure they stand out. I am also adjusting the text styling for this specific container.\n\n\n**Refining Visual Harmony**\n\nI\'m now integrating stylistic improvements to harmonize the Actionable Vectors and Emotional Tone sections. I\'ve updated the border colors, refined the overall background, and focused on maintaining consistency in the visual presentation. Specifically, I\'m integrating the updated list presentation in `/src/components/AISummarySheet.tsx`, including font, size and the bullet markers.\n\n\n**Updating Emotional Tone**\n\nI\'m now focusing on the Emotional Tone list. I\'m updating this container to match the overall visual presentation of the Actionable Vectors section, integrating the same font and style. I\'ve switched the text to sans-serif and am refining list markers and spacing for a more cohesive look in the `AISummarySheet.tsx` file. I am working on lines 196 to 226 of the file.\n\n\n**Styling Final Button Elements**\n\nI\'m now focusing on the footer buttons within `/src/components/AISummarySheet.tsx`, specifically the \"Refine Summary\", \"Copy to Clipboard\", and \"Share\" buttons. I\'m aiming for a visually cohesive and high-end aesthetic. I am updating their text colors and borders to match the overall design. I\'m focusing on the integration of these UI elements.\n\n\n\n**Integrating Button Styles**\n\nI\'m now integrating the button styles in the footer, which is the \"R