  planner_response {
    modified_response: "I have successfully applied the **Vibrant Palette** design theme to the SoulJournal application, ensuring all existing functionality, real-time Gemini integration, and interactive components are preserved. \n\n### Design Overview\n- **Visual Identity & Atmosphere**:\n  - Replaced the soft lavender backgrounds with a warm, elegant bright ivory/cream texture (`#FDFCFB`) paired with high-contrast slate borders (`#1E293B`) to reflect the layout architecture of the reference devices.\n  - Introduced premium, ultra-bold branding elements with the hallmark signature dot (`SoulJournal.`, `Today.`, `Today\'s Reflections.`) using robust sans-serif display typography.\n- **Vibrant Gradients**:\n  - Leveraged a gorgeous `indigo-500` via `purple-500` to `rose-500` gradient for key active elements: the onboarding icon base, the calendar\'s selected day highlight, the floating action buttons, and the atmospheric visual card inside the AI summary sheet.\n- **High-Contrast Elements & Color Coding**:\n  - Configured vibrant accents on cards with a colored sidebar structure (such as indigo for Milestones, rose for Actionable Vectors, and amber for Emotional Tone) to present an elegant categorization scheme.\n  - Redesigned action chips and interactive components with smooth active scaling animations to make navigation feel highly responsive and luxurious."
