    modified_response: "I have successfully implemented a fully functional bottom tab navigation system for **SoulJournal**, matching the high-end interaction and aesthetic patterns of native mobile apps:\n\n- **Stitch-Inspired Bottom Tab Navigation**: Added a floating, sticky bottom tab bar inside the mobile phone chassis with custom responsive micro-animations:\n  - **Journal Tab** (`history_edu`): Allows writing text reflections, choosing custom emotional moods, dictating via simulated real-time smart vocal transcription, and viewing the daily feed.\n  - **Stats Tab** (`query_stats`): Features a custom, highly interactive radial SVG ring gauge displaying real-time energetic charge. Includes adjustable counters for steps and sleep, and logs real-time metrics for total words composed and dominant frequencies.\n  - **Confidant Tab** (`auto_awesome`): Integrates the AI companion directly within the core flow instead of a blocking drawer. Features milestones, actionable steps, dynamic mood balances, and a live chat input to refine summaries with the real server-side Gemini model.\n- **Vibrant Theme Synchronizations**: Cohesive transitions, high-contrast typography, and soft visual gradients paired to elevate the digital journal experience."
